    public class FirebaseService
extends com.google.firebase.messaging.FirebaseMessagingService
    Background service to get fire-base messages. All type of fire-base push notification will be received here. If notification is to assign new task to the driver, then OpenTicketFragment will be opened to show the task details. In this scenario, there are two cases. First is if application's MainActivity is opened and other is application is in background or closed.
    If MainActivity is open then we are free to load OpenTicketFragment anytime. But on the darker side, If application is not active, A Notification has been created to notify user for the new Task/Ticket.
